translate portuguese ss1_cdbb8564:

    # "Ms. Welch starts class by handing out the tests that we did the previous week."
    "A Sra. Welch começa a aula distribuindo os testes que fizemos na semana anterior."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:13
translate portuguese ss1_5d9d5d63:

    # gg "How did you do?"
    gg "Como te saíste?"

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:14
translate portuguese ss1_0dbc34a9:

    # pc "I aced it. Perfect A+"
    pc "Fui de lixo. A+ perfeito."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:16
translate portuguese ss1_9872da7c:

    # gg "Wow, nice! I might need to study with you sometime."
    gg "Uau, fixe! Talvez precise de estudar contigo um dia destes."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:20
translate portuguese ss1_edc93756:

    # "She turns back to the front and then Ms. Welch starts lecturing."
    "Ela volta-se para a frente e a Sra. Welch começa a dar a aula."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:23
translate portuguese ss1_ac33b73f:

    # gg "Can't wait."
    gg "Mal posso esperar."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:24
translate portuguese ss1_34213f63:

    # "After that, Ms. Welch starts lecturing and we both turn to the front and try to stay awake."
    "Depois disso, a Sra. Welch começa a dar a aula e nós os dois viramo-nos para a frente e tentamos manter-nos acordados."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:28
translate portuguese ss1_38327323:

    # "Ms. Welch goes on and on about the questions that were missed the most on the test."
    "A Sra. Welch fala sem parar sobre as perguntas em que mais falhámos no teste."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:29
translate portuguese ss1_60ee67bc:

    # "Then she starts in on what we will be covering with the next test which will be next week."
    "Depois, ela começa a falar sobre o que vamos ver na próxima prova, que será na próxima semana."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:30
translate portuguese ss1_18c2b08f:

    # "I try to pay attention, but it's hard when I really just don't care about the subject matter at all, and my mind is going everywhere else."
    "Tento prestar atenção, mas é difícil quando realmente não me interessa nada o assunto e a minha mente está a vaguear por todo o lado."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:32
translate portuguese ss1_b4a5181e:

    # "I think about my dad. I think about work. I think about what Ms. Welch would look like without that dress on."
    "Penso no meu pai. Penso no trabalho. Penso em como seria a Sra. Welch sem aquele vestido vestido."

# game/Scenes/School/SocialStudies/ss1.rpy:34
translate portuguese ss1_5a4862a5:

